graph LR
    User[User / Visitor]
    Admin[System Administrator]
    
    subgraph DFD Level 1: Core System Processes
        Process1[1.0 Session Auth]
        Process2[2.0 URL Scan Processor]
        Process3[3.0 Quiz Engine]
        Process4[4.0 PDF Report Generator]
        Process5[5.0 Admin Control Board]
    end
    
    subgraph Data Stores
        DB_Users[(Users Table)]
        DB_Scans[(Scan History Table)]
        DB_Quizzes[(Quiz Results Table)]
        DB_Logs[(Admin Logs Table)]
    end
    
    %% Inputs/Outputs
    User -->|Enter Credentials| Process1
    Process1 <-->|Verify / Write User| DB_Users
    
    User -->|Submit URL Link| Process2
    Process2 -->|Extract Features & Run ML| Process2
    Process2 <-->|Fetch / Record Scan| DB_Scans
    
    User -->|Submit MCQ Answers| Process3
    Process3 <-->|Record Score & Certificate| DB_Quizzes
    Process3 -->|Trigger Certificate| Process4
    
    User -->|Click Download PDF| Process4
    Process4 <-->|Read Scan Details| DB_Scans
    Process4 -->|Output PDF Stream| User
    
    Admin -->|Login Credentials| Process1
    Admin -->|Request Delete User| Process5
    Process5 <-->|Delete Records| DB_Users
    Process5 <-->|Fetch Logs| DB_Scans
    Process5 <-->|Write Audit Actions| DB_Logs
